  line `P ROVISIONS AS TO CERTAIN CORPORATIONS`
  line `S ECTIONS`
  line `68. Provisions for various companies and corporations.`
  line `69. Continuance of arrangements in regard to generation and supply of electric power and supply of`
  line water.
  line `70. Provisions as to Andhra Pradesh State Financial Corporation.`
  line `71. Certain provisions for companies.`
  line `72. Temporary provisions as to continuance of certain existing road transport permits.`
  line `73. Special provisions relating to, retrenchment compensation in certain cases.`
  line `74. Special provision as to income - tax.`
  line `75. Continuance of facilities in certain State institutions.`
