  line `P ROVISIONS AS TO SERVICES`
  line `76. Provisions relating to All - India Services.`
  line `77. Provisions relating to other services.`
  line `78. Other provisions relating to services.`
  line `79. Provisions as to continuance of officers in same post.`
  line `80. Advisory committees.`
  line `81. Power of Central Government to give directions.`
  line `82. Provision for employees of Public Sector Undertakings, etc.`
  line `83. Provisions as to State Public Service Commission.`
  line `PART IX`
  line `M ANAGEMENT AND DEVELOPMENT OF WATER RESOURCES`
  line `84. Apex Council for Godavari and Krishna river water resources and their Management Boards.`
  line `85. Constitution and functions of River Management Board.`
  line `86. Staff of the Management Board.`
  line `87. Jurisdiction of Board.`
  line `88. Power of Board to make regulations.`
  line `89. Allocation of water resources.`
  line `90. Polavaram Irrigation Project to be a national project.`
  line `91. Arrangements on Tungabhadra Board.`
  line `PART X`
