obj_root_law_sections_32_content:
  string
  line 32
  line `THE FIRST SCHEDULE`
  line `( See section 13)`
  line `( i ) Of the five sitting members whose term of office will expire on 9th April, 2014,namely, Shri T.`
  line `Subbarami Reddy, Shri Nandi Yellaiah, Shri Mohammed Ali Khan,Smt. T. Ratna Bai and Shri K.V.P.`
  line `Ramachandra Rao, such two as the Chairman of the Councilof States may determine by drawing lots shall`
  line `be deemed to have been elected to fill two ofthe seven seats allotted to the State of Telangana and the`
  line `other three sitting members shallbe deemed to have been elected to fill three of the eleven seats allotted to`
  line `the State of Andhra Pradesh.`
  line `( ii ) Of the six sitting members whose term of office will expire on 21st June, 2016, namely, Shri`
  line `Jesudasu Seelam, Shri Jairam Ramesh, Shri N. Janardhana Reddy,Shri V. Hanumantha Rao, Smt. Gundu`
  line `Sudharani and Shri Y.S. Chowdary, such two as theChairman of the Council of States may determine by`
  line `drawing lots shall be deemed to havebeen elected to fill two of the seats allotted to the State of Telangana`
  line `and the other foursitting members shall be deemed to have been elected to fill four of the seats allotted to`
  line `theState of Andhra Pradesh.`
  line `( iii ) Of the six sitting m embers representing the State of Andhra Pradesh whose termof office will`
  line `expire on 2nd April, 2018, namely, Shri Ananda Baskar Rapolu, Shri K. Chiranjeevi,Shri Palvai`
  line `Govardhana Reddy, Smt. Renuka Chowdhury, Shri T. Devender Goud and Shri C.M. Ramesh, such three`
  line `as the Chairman of the Council of States may determine bydrawing lots shall be deemed to have been`
  line `elected to fill three of the seats allotted to theState of Telangana and the other three sitting members shall`
  line `be deemed to have been elected to fill the three of the seats allotted to the State of Andhra Pradesh.`
  line `( iv ) The term of one seat which is to expire on 9th April, 2014 and has become vacantdue to`
  line `resignation of Shri Nandamuri Harikrishna on 22nd August, 201 4, shall be allotted tothe State of Andhra`
  line Pradesh.
