  line 34
  line `( v ) after serial number 24 relating to Tamil Nadu and the entries relating thereto, the following`
  line `shall be inserted, namely: ––`
  line `1 2 3 4 5 6 7`
  line `“25. Telangana - - - 119 19 1 2”;`
  line `( vi ) serial numbers 25 to 28 shall be renumbered as serial numbers 26 to 29, respectively.`
  line `3. For Schedule III, the following shall be substituted, namely: ––`
  line `“SCHEDULE – III`
  line `ANDHRA PRADESH`
  line `TABLE A – ASSEMBLY CONSTITUENCIES`
  line `Sl.No. & Name Extent of Assembly Constituencies`
  line `1 2`
  line `1 — DISTRICT: SRIKAKULAM`
