  line `4. Pathapatnam Pathapatnam, Meliaputti, L.N. Pet, Kothur and H iramandalam`
  line Mandals.
  line `5. Srikakulam Gara and Srikakulam Mandals.`
  line `6. Amadalavalasa Amadalavalasa, Ponduru, Sarubujjili and Burja Mandals.`
  line `7. Etcherla G. Sigadam, Laveru, Ranastalam and Etcherla Mandals.`
  line `8. Narasannapeta Jalumuru, Narasannapeta, Saravakota and Polaki Mandals.`
  line `9. Rajam (SC) Vangara, Regidi Amadalavalasa, Rajam and Santhakaviti Mandals.`
  line `10. Palakonda (ST) Seethampeta, Bhamini, Palakonda and Veeraghattam Mandals.`
  line `2 — DISTRICT: VIZIANAGARAM`
  line `11. Kurupam (ST) Kurupam, Gummalakshmipuram, Jiyyammavalasa, Komarada and`
  line `Garugubilli Mandals.`
  line `12. Parvathipuram (SC) Parvathipuram, Seethanagaram and Balijipeta Mandals.`
  line `13. Salur (ST) Salur, Pachipenta, Mentada and Makkuva Mandals.`
  line `14. Bobbili Bobbili, Ramabhadrapuram, Badangi and Therlam Mandals.`
  line `15. Cheepurupalli Merakamudidam, Garividi, Cheepurupalli and GurlaMandals.`
  line `16. Gajapathinagaram Gajapathinagaram, Bondapalli, Gantyada and Dattirajeru Mandals; and`
  line `Vizinigiri, Thandrangi, Jannivalasa, Venne, Sasanapalli, Attada,`
  line `Bheemasingi, Somayajulapalem, Lotlapalli, Mokhasa Kothavalasa,`
  line `Kumaram and Annamrajupeta villages of Jami Mandal.`
  line `17. Nellimarla Nellimarla, Pusapatirega, Denkada and Bhogapuram Mandals.`
  line `18. Vizianagaram Vizianagaram Mandal.`
  line `19. Srungavarapukota Srungavarapukota, Vepada, Lakkavarapukota and Kothavalasa`
  line `Mandals; and Jami Mandal (Except 12 village s i.e. Vizinigiri,`
  line `Thandrangi, Jannivalasa, Venne, Sasanapalli, Attada, Bheemasingi,`
  line `Somayajulapalem, Lotlapalli, M okhasa Kothavalasa, Kumaram and`
  line `Annamrajupeta).`
