  line `108. Bhupalpalle Mogullapalle, Chityal, Bhupalpalle, Ghanpur (Mulug), Regonda and`
  line `Shayampet Mandals.`
  line `109. Mulug (ST) Venkatapur, Eturnagaram, Mangapet, Tadvai, Kothaguda,`
  line `Govindaraopet and Mulug Mandals.`
  line `10 — DISTRICT: KHAMMAM`
  line `1 [ 110. Pinapaka (ST) Pinapaka, Manuguru, Gundala, Aswapuram Mandals and`
  line `Bhurgumpadu Mandal excluding the Revenue Villages of`
  line `Seetharamanagram, Sridhara Velair, Gumpanapalli, Ganapavaram,`
  line `Ibrahimpet and Ravigudem (big). ]`
  line `111. Yellandu (ST) Kamepalle, Yellandu, Bayyaram, Tekulapalle and Garla Mandals.`
  line `112. Khammam Khammam Mandal.`
  line `113. Palair Thirumalayapalem, Kusumanchi, Khammam Rural and`
  line `Nelakondapalle Mandals.`
  line `114. Madhira (SC) Mudigonda, Chinthakani, Bonakal, Madhira andYerrupalem`
  line Mandals.
  line `115. Wyra (ST) Enkuru, Konijerla, Singareni, Julurpadu and WyraMandals.`
  line `116. Sathupalle (SC) Sathupalle, Penuballi, Kallur, Tallada and Vemsoor Mandals.`
  line `117. Kothagudem Kothagudem and Palwancha Mandals.`
  line `1 [ 118. Aswaraopeta (ST) Mulikalapalle, Chandrugonda, Aswaraopeta and Dammapeta`
  line Mandals.
  line `119. Bhadrachalam (ST) Wazeed, Venkatapuram, Cherla, Dummugudem Mandals and`
  line `Bhadrachalam Revenue Village.]`
  line `1. Subs by notificationNo. G.S.R. 311(E), dated 23 - 4 - 2015.`
