obj_root_law_sections_49_content:
  string
  line 49
  line `TABLE B – PARLIAMENTARY CONSTITUENCIES`
  line `Sl.No. & Name Extent of Parliamentary Constituencies`
  line `1 2`
  line `1. ADILABAD (ST) 1 - Sirpur, 5 - Asifabad (ST), 6 - Khanapur (ST), 7 - Adilabad,`
  line `8 - Boath (ST), 9 - Nirmal and 10 - Mudhole.`
  line `2. PEDDAPALLE (SC) 2 Chennur (SC), 3 Bellampalle (SC), 4 Mancherial,`
  line `22 Dharmapuri (SC), 23 Ramagundam, 24 Manthani and`
  line `25 Peddapalle.`
  line `3. KARIMNAGAR 26 - Karimnagar, 27 - Choppadandi (SC), 28 - Vemulawada,`
  line `29 - Sircilla, 30 - Manakondur (SC), 31 - Huzurabad and`
  line `32 - Husnabad.`
  line `4. NIZAMABAD 1 - Armur, 2 - Bodhan, 3 - Nizamabad (Urban),`
  line `4 - Nizamabad (Rural), 5 - Balkonda, 6 - Koratla and`
  line `7 - Jagtial.`
  line `5. ZAHIRABAD 13 Jukkal (SC), 14 Banswada, 15 Yellareddy, 16 Kamareddy,`
  line `35 Narayankhed, 36 Andole (SC) and 38 Zahirabad (SC).`
  line `6. MEDAK 8 - Siddipet, 9 - Medak, 10 - Narsapur, 11 - Sangareddy,`
  line `12 - Patancheru, 1 3 - Dubbak and 14 - Gajwel.`
  line `7. MALKAJGIRI 15 - Medchal, 16 - Malkajgiri, 17 - Qutbullapur, 18 - Kukatpalle,`
  line `19 - Uppal, 20 - Lal Bahadur Nagar and 2 1 - SecunderabadCantt.`
  line `(SC).`
  line `8. SECUNDERABAD 57 Musheerabad, 59 Amberpet, 60 Khairatabad, 61 Jubilee`
  line `Hills, 62 Sanathnagar, 63 Nampally and 70 Secunderabad.`
  line `9. HYDERABAD 22 - Malakpet, 23 - Karwan, 24 - Goshamaha l, 25 - Charminar,`
  line `26 - Chandrayangutta, 27 - Yakutpura and 28 - Bahadurpura.`
  line `10. CHEVELLA 29 - Maheswaram, 30 - Rajendranagar, 31 - Serilingampally,`
  line `3 2 - Chevella (SC), 33 - Pargi, 34 - Vicarabad (SC) and`
  line `3 5 - Tandur.`
  line `11. MAHBUBNAGAR 36 - Kodangal, 3 7 - Narayanpet, 38 - Mahbubnagar,`
  line `39 - Jadcherla, 40 - Devarkadra, 41 - Makthal and`
  line `4 2 - Shadnagar.`
  line `12. NAGARKURNOOL (SC) 78 Wanaparthy, 79 Gadwal, 80 Alampur (SC),`
  line `81 Nagarkurnool, 82 Achampet (SC), 83 Kalwakurthy and`
  line `85 Kollapur.`
  line `13. NALGONDA 43 - Devarakonda (ST), 44 - Nagarjuna Sagar,`
  line `45 - Miryalaguda, 46 - Huzurnagar, 47 - Kodad, 48 - Suryapet`
  line `and 49 - Nalgonda.`
  line `14. BHONGIR 48 Ibrahimpatnam, 93 Munugode, 94 Bhongir,`
  line `95 Nakrekal (SC), 96 Thungathurthi (SC), 97 Alair and`
  line `98 Jangoan.`
  line `15. WARANGAL(SC) 50 - Ghanpur (Station) (SC), 5 1 - Palakurthi, 52 - Parkal,`
  line `53 - Warangal West, 54 - Warangal East, 55 - Wardhannapet`
  line `(SC) and 56 - Bhupalpalle.`
  line `16. MAHABUBABAD (ST) 101 Dornakal (ST), 102 Mahabubabad (ST), 103 Narsampet,`
  line `109 Mulug (ST), 110 Pinapaka (ST), 111 Yellandu (ST) and`
  line `119 Bhadrachalam (ST).`
  line `17. KHAMMAM 57 - Khammam, 58 - Palair, 59 - Madhira (SC),`
  line `60 - Wyra (ST), 6 1 - Sathupalle (SC), 63 - Kothagudem and 63 -`
  line `Aswaraopeta (ST).`
  line `NOTE: Any reference in Table A to a CT, OG, Mandal and Villages or other territorial division shall`
  line `betaken to mean the area comprised within that CT, OG, Mandal and Villages or other`
  line `territorialdivision as on the 15th day of February, 2004. Further, any reference in Table – A, to`
  line `wards inmunicipal areas shall be taken to mean the areas as defined in the Census of India`
  line 2001Report.”.
