  line 50
  line `THE THIRD SCHEDULE`
  line `( See section 24)`
  line `PART I`
  line `MODIFICATION IN THE DELIMITATION OF COUNCIL CONSTITUENCIES`
  line `(ANDHRA PRADESH) ORDER, 2006`
  line `For the Table appended to the Delimitation of Council Constituencies (Andhra Pradesh) Order, 2006, the`
  line `following Table shall be substituted, namely: ––`
  line “TABLE
  line `Name of Constituency Extent of Constituency Number ofseats`
  line `Local Authorities ’ Constituencies`
  line `1. Srikakulam Local Authorities Srikakulam 1`
  line `2. Vizianagaram Local Authorities Vizianagaram 1`
  line `3. Visakhapatnam Local Authorities Visakhapatnam 2`
  line `4. East Godavari Local Authorities East Godavari 2`
  line `5. West Godavari Local Authorities West Godavari 2`
  line `6. Krishna Local Authorities Krishna 2`
  line `7. Guntur Local Authorities Guntur 2`
  line `8. Prakasam Local Authorities Prakasam 1`
  line `9. Nellore Local Authorities Nellore 1`
  line `10. Chittoor Local Authorities Chittoor 2`
  line `11. Kadapa Local Authorities Kadapa 1`
  line `12. Anantapur Local Authorities Anantapur 2`
  line `13. Kurnool Local Authorities Kurnool 1`
  line `Graduates’ Constituencies`
  line `1. Srikakulam - Vizianagaram - Srikakulam, Vizianagaram, 1`
  line `Visakhapatnam Graduate Visakhapatnam`
  line `2. East - West Godavari Graduates East - West Godavari 1`
  line `3. Krishna - Guntur Graduates Krishna - Guntur 1`
  line `4. Prakasam - Nellore - Chittoor Graduates Prakasam - Nellore - Chitt o or 1`
  line `5. Kadapa - Anantapur - Kurnool Graduates Kadapa - Anantapur - Kurnool 1”.`
  line `Teacher's Constituencies`
  line `1. Srikakulam - Vizianagaram - Srikakulam, Vizianagaram, 1`
  line `Visakhapatnam Teachers Visakhapatnam`
  line `2. East - West Godavari Teachers East - West Godavari 1`
  line `3. Krishna - Guntur Teachers Krishna - Guntur 1`
  line `4. Prakasam - Nellore - Chittoor Teachers Prakasam - Nellore - Chittoor 1`
  line `5. Kadapa - Anantapur - Kurnool Teachers Kadapa - Anantapur - Kurnool 1”.`
