obj_root_law_sections_51_content:
  string
  line 51
  line `PART II`
  line `1. This Order may be called the Delimitation of Council Constituencies (Telangana) Order, 2014.`
  line `2. The costituencies into which the State of Telangana shall be divided for thepurpose of elections to the`
  line `Legislative Council of the State from ( a ) the local authorities'constituencies, ( b ) the graduates'`
  line `constituencies, and ( c ) the teachers' constituencies in thesaid State, the extent of each such constituency`
  line `and the number of seats allotted to eachsuch constituency shall be as shown in the following Table: —`
  line TABLE
  line `Name of Constituency Extent of Constituency Number ofseats`
  line `* Local Authorities’ Constituencies`
  line `1. Mahbubnagar Local Authorities Mahbubnagar 1`
  line `2. Ranga Reddy Local Authorities Ranga Reddy 1`
  line `3. Hyderabad Local Authorities Hyderabad 2`
  line `4. Medak Local Authorities Medak 1`
  line `5. Nizamabad Local Authorities Nizamabad 1`
  line `6. Adilabad Local Authorities Adilabad 1`
  line `7. Karimnagar Local Authorities Karimnagar 1`
  line `8. Warangal Local Authorities Warangal 1`
  line `9. Khammam Local Authorities Khammam 1`
  line `10. Nalgonda Local Authorities Nalgonda 1`
  line `Graduates’ Constituencies`
  line `1. Mahbubnagar - Ranga Reddy - Mahbubnagar - Ranga 1`
  line `Hyderabad Graduates Reddy Hyderabad`
  line `2. Medak - Nizamabad - Adilabad - Medak - Nizamabad - 1`
  line `Karimnagar Graduates Adilabad - Karimnagar`
  line `3. Warangal - Khammam - Warangal - Khammam - 1`
  line `Nalgonda Graduates Nalgonda`
  line `Teacher’ s Constituencies`
  line `1. Mahbubnagar - Ranga Reddy - Mahbubnagar - Ranga 1`
  line `Hyderabad Teachers Reddy Hyderabad`
  line `2. Medak - Nizamabad - Adilabad - Medak - Nizamabad - 1`
  line `Karimnagar Teachers Adilabad - Karimnagar`
  line `3. Warangal - Khammam - Warangal - Khammam - 1`
  line `Nalgonda Teachers Nalgonda`
  line `* See notification No. G.S.R. 313(E), dated 23 - 4 - 2015.`
