obj_root_law_sections_52_content:
  string
  line 52
  line `THE FOURTH SCHEDULE`
  line `[ See section 22( 2 )]`
  line `List of members of the Legislative Council of successor States of Andhra Pradesh and Telangana: —`
  line `Legislative Council of Andhra Pradesh:`
  line `Members of Local Authorities Constituencies:`
  line `(1) Ilapuram Venkaiah, (2) Pothula Rama Rao, (3) D.V. Suryanarayana Raju, (4) Narayana Reddy`
  line `Chadipiralla, (5) Boddu Bhaskara Ramarao, (6) Angara Ramamohan, (7) Dr. DesaiThippa Reddy, M.S.,`
  line `(8) Meka Seshu Babu, (9) Peerukatla Viswa Prasada Rao, (10) NarayanaReddy Vakati, (11) Mettu`
  line `Govinda Reddy.`
  line `Members of Graduates’ Constituencies:`
  line `(1) Boddu Nageswara Rao, (2) Kalidindi Ravi Kiran Varma, (3) M.V.S. Sarma, (4) Yandapalli`
  line `Srinivasulu Reddy, (5) Dr. Geyanand M.`
  line `Members of Teachers’ Constituencies.`
  line `(1) Gade Srinivasulu Naidu, (2) K.V.V. Satyanarayana Raju, (3) K.S. Lakshmana Rao,`
  line `(4) Balasubrahmany am Vitapu, (5) Bachala Pullaiah, 1 [(6) Kantheti Satya narayana Raju, (7) T. Ratna`
  line `Bai ].`
  line `Nominated Members.`
  line `(1) Jupudi Prabhakar Rao, (2) Balashali Indira, (3) Dr. A. Chakrapani, (4) R. Reddeppa Reddy,`
  line `(5) Shaik Hussain.`
  line `Members elected from Legislative Assembly Constituencies.`
  line `(1) K. Veerabhadra Swamy, (2) A. Lakshmi Siva Kumari, (3) R. Padma Raju, (4) Paladugu Venkata`
  line `Rao, (5) Mohammad Jani, (6) N. Rajakumari, (7) Y. Ramakrishnudu, (8) S. Basava Punnaiah,`
  line `(9) A. Appa Rao, (10) P.J. Chandrasekhara Rao, (11) B. Changal Rayudu,(12) P. Samanthakamani,`
  line `(13) C. Ramachandraiah, (14) S.V. Satish Kumar Reddy, (15) G. Thippe Swamy, (16) M. Sudhakar Babu.`
  line `Legislative Council of Telangana:`
  line `Members of Local Authorities Constituencies.`
  line `(1) Nethi Vidya Sagar, (2) V. Bhoopal Reddy, (3) Arikala Narsa Reddy, (4) Potla Nageswar Rao,`
  line `(5) T. Bhanu Prasad Rao, (6) S. Jagadeeshwar Reddy, (7) Sri M.S. Prabhakar Rao, (8) Sri Patnam`
  line `Narender Reddy, (9) Syed Aminul Hasan Jafri.`
  line `Members of Graduates’ Constituencies:`
  line `(1) Dr. K. Nageshwar, (2) Kapilavai Dileep Kumar, (3) K. Swamy Goud.`
  line `Members of Teachers’ Constituencies.`
  line `(1) Pathuri Sudhakar Reddy, (2) Poola Ravinder, (3) Katepally Janardhan Reddy.`
  line `Nominated Members.`
  line `(1) D. Rajeshwar Rao, (2) Farooq Hussain, (3) B. Venkata Rao.`
  line `Elected by Members of Legislative Assembly`
  line `* (1) K.R. Amos, (2) Mohammad Ali Shabbir, (3) K. Yadava Reddy, (4) V. GangadharGoud,`
  line `(5) T. Santosh Kumar, (6) N. Rajalingam, (7) D. Srinivas, (8) M. Ranga Reddy, (9) P. Sudhakar Reddy,`
  line `(10) B. Lakshmi Narayana, (11) Mohammad Saleem, (12) B. Venkateswarlu, (13) Peer Shabbir Ahmed,`
  line `(14) Mohammad Mahmood Ali, (15) Syed Altaf Hyder Razvi.`
  line `1. Ins. by notification No. G.S.R. 725(E), dated 14 - 10 - 2014.`
  line `* Omitted by notificationNo. G.S.R. 312(E), dated 23 - 4 - 2015.`
  line `The seat vacated by Shri K. R. Amos shall cease to exist and shall not be filled up in accordance with sub - clause ( b ) of clause ( i )`
  line `of sub - section ( 2 ) of section 23 of the Andhra Pradesh Reorganisation Act, 2014.`
