  line `THE FIFTH SCHEDULE`
  line `( See section 28)`
  line `In the Constitution (Scheduled Castes) Order, 1950, ––`
  line `( 1 ) in paragraph 2, for the figures “XXIV”, the figures “XXV” shall besubstituted;`
  line `( 2 ) in the Schedule, ––`
  line `( a ) in PART I relating to Andhra Pradesh, item number 9, shall be omitted;`
  line `( b ) after Part XXIV, the following Part shall be inserted, namely: ––`
  line `“PART XXV. –– Telangana`
  line `1. Adi Andhra`
  line `2. Adi Dravida`
  line `3. Anamuk`
  line `4. Aray Mala`
  line `5. Arundhatiya`
  line `6. Arwa Mala`
  line `7. Bariki`
  line `8. Bavuri`
