  line 55
  line `THE SIXTH SCHEDULE`
  line `( See section 29)`
  line `AMENDMENTS TO THE CONSTITUTION (SCHEDULED TRIBES) ORDER, 1950`
  line `In the Constitution (Scheduled Tribes) Order, 1950, ––`
  line `( 1 ) in paragraph 2, for the figures “XXII”, the figures “XXIII” shall besubstituted;`
  line `( 2 ) in the Schedule, ––`
  line `(a) in PART I relating to Andhra Pradesh, ––`
  line `( i ) in item number 20, the brackets and words “(excluding Adilabad, Hyderabad, Karimnagar,`
  line `Khammam, Mahbubnagar, Medak, Nalgonda, Nizamabad and Warangal districts)” shall be`
  line omitted;
  line `( ii ) item number 30 and the entries relating thereto shall be omitted;`
  line `(b) after Part XXIV, the following Part shall be inserted, namely: ––`
  line `“PART XXV. –– Telangana`
  line `1. Andh, Sadhu Andh`
  line `2. Bagata`
  line `3. Bhil`
  line `4. Chenchu`
  line `5. Gadabas, Bodo Gadaba, Gutob Gadaba, Kallayi Gadaba, Parangi Gadaba, Kathera`
  line `Gadaba, Kapu Gadaba`
  line `6. Gond, Naikpod, Rajgond, Koitur`
  line `7. Goudu (in the Agency tracts)`
  line `8. Hill Reddis`
  line `9. Jatapus`
  line `10. Kammara`
  line `11. Kattunayakan`
  line `12. Kolam, Kolawar`
  line `13. Konda Dhoras, Kubi`
  line `14. Konda Kapus`
  line `15. Kondareddis`
  line `16. Kondhs, Kodi, Kodhu, Desaya Kondhs, Dongria Kondhs, Kuttiya Kondhs, Tikiria`
  line `Kondhs, Yenity Kondhs, Kuvinga`
  line `17. Kotia, Bentho Oriya, Bartika, Duli a, Hol y a, Sanrona, Sidhopaiko`
  line `18. Koya, Doli Koya, Gutta Koya, Kammara Koya, Musara Koya, Oddi Koya, Pattidi`
  line `Koya, Rajah, Rasha Koya, Lingadhari Koya (ordinary), Kottu Koya, Bhine Koya, Rajkoya`
  line `19. Kulia`
  line `20. Manna Dhora`
  line `21. Mukha Dhora, Nooka Dhora`
  line `22. Nayaks (in the Agency tracts)`
  line `23. Pardhan`
