obj_root_law_sections_57_content:
  string
  line 57
  line `THE SEVENTH SCHEDULE`
  line `( See section 52)`
  line `LIST OF FUNDS`
  line `A. Provident Funds, Pension Funds, Insurance Funds`
  line `1. Contributory Provident Fund Work - charged 50% N.R.S.`
  line `2. All India Ser v i ce Provident Fund.`
  line `3. Deposits of Zilla Praja Parishads out of Provident Fund contribution.`
  line `4. General Provident Fund (Regular).`
  line `5. Andhra Pradesh Class IV Govt. Servants Family Pension Fund.`
